node.text:
[Meta Singapore] - A star-studded lunch from @metasingapore , thank you @singaporeliciouz for the yummy surprise lunch.
.
We had the Wagyu Beef Don, Iberico Pork Don and Gimbap.
.
To order visit https://www.metarestaurant.sg
You are welcome! Hope you enjoyed it as much as we do!!! 🙌🏻
